summary: Imagine Peter getting MJ and Ned such amazing gifts for their birthdays but when Peters birthday rolls around they have no idea...
body:
Imagine Peter getting MJ and Ned such amazing gifts for their birthdays but when Peters birthday rolls around they have no idea what to get him. So they hand Peter a conjoined gift and the whole time he’s unwrapping it they’re apologizing and saying it’s stupid and awful.

It’s a little statue that says #1 mom

Ned: I mean like we said it’s awful

MJ: yeah it’s dumb we can think of something better I- Peter?

Peter with tears in his eyes: I- I love it so much :,)

summary: PPSS #42: Let’s meet Debra, Peter’s grad school buddy with...hoo boy, literally the worst self-esteem I have ever seen in a...
caption:
PPSS #42:

Let’s meet Debra, Peter’s grad school buddy with…hoo boy, literally the worst self-esteem I have ever seen in a comic.

Peter, of course, will manage to make her feel even worse throughout this issue by abandoning her immediately after this panel.

Deb’s cute. I hope she gets some help and learns to appreciate and take care of herself. I’ll bring her back in my run on All-New, All-Different Frightful Four.

body:
Favorite bois

I was tagged by @acherik to do this, I actually remembered to do something I was tagged in! Miracle.

Write your top 10 favorite male characters (each can be from different fandom but not required) in no particular order:

1. Alexander Summers/Havok (Alexander dam he thick ~jacksfilms 2017)

2.Peter Parker/Spider-man (shy,nerdy obviously bi spider-boy)

3. Wade Wilson/Deadpool (merc with a mouth who spreads pansexual awareness)

4. Hank McCoy/Beast (big fluffy boy who needs more love)

5. Big Daddies- Bioshock (I really love their designs and are fucking badass. Bioshock 2 is my favorite of all 3 games because you get to play as a big daddy)

6. Wheatley- Portal (the moron who got shot into space)

7. Craig and Tweek- south park (I know this is cheating but I don’t really like one over the other, they are both beautiful boys in a relationship)

8. Pip Pirrup- South Park (you all forget him but this british boy will always be in my heart)

9. Beast- beauty and the beast (this is a weird one, I know. But Beauty and the best IS MY FAVORITE disney tale. I loved the beast and honestly didn’t even want to see him turn human again)

10. Pyramid head- Silent hill (another weird one, I LOVEEEE horror movies. And pyrimad head is one of my favorite representations of sexual frustration and aggression, the the player he is as real as you want him to be. I am a psychology student so it makes me appreciate him that much more)

I tagggg @comicus-peixes , @fflaminlo , @spidertea-art , and ah..you..yes you reading this.
